      <odd id="aspace_674e40f690956a33d5cd75f4e3fb4480">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 40 (YRG 40), Records of Yale clubs, societies, and organizations.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_76b9db766eeb7afa347065dfd443680c">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Yale Record Records (RU 519). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_c4e5ace708940f40e01fdfca6c5983b5">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by record type.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_e6bc428af195812402632345eb279b85">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale Record, a student publication, was established in 1872.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_25a97d0ee3aef528e1f6abcd9dcb5bc0">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, manuscripts, legal and financial papers, and cartoons documenting the Yale Record.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
